{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01TcfNRn45X4G8wJzQCm8HEA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Cg4EkQsHXQjB92C3DoyZHW","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create Spring Boot core files","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE Petclinic application to Spring Boot. I need you to create the following files. The base directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nIMPORTANT: First, remove all old Jakarta EE-specific directories and files that are no longer needed:\n- Delete the directory: src/main/liberty/ (and all contents)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/runtimes/ (and all contents) \n- Delete the directory: src/main/webapp/ (and all contents - JSF views are replaced by Thymeleaf)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/views/ (JSF framework views)\n\nThen create these files:\n\n1. **src/main/resources/application.properties**\n```\nspring.application.name=petclinic\nserver.port=8080\nserver.servlet.context-path=/petclinic\n\n# PostgreSQL\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/petclinic_jakartaee_liberty\nspring.datasource.username=petclinic_jakartaee\nspring.datasource.password=petclinic_jakartaeepwd\nspring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.postgresql.Driver\n\n# JPA\nspring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create\nspring.jpa.show-sql=true\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.dialect=org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQLDialect\nspring.jpa.defer-datasource-initialization=true\n\n# Initialize database\nspring.sql.init.mode=always\nspring.sql.init.platform=postgresql\n\n# Thymeleaf\nspring.thymeleaf.cache=false\n\n# Actuator\nmanagement.endpoints.web.exposure.include=health,info\nmanagement.endpoint.health.show-details=always\n\n# Logging\nlogging.level.org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic=INFO\n```\n\n2. **src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/PetclinicSpringApplication.java**\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic;\n\nimport org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication;\nimport org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.SpringBootApplication;\n\n@SpringBootApplication\npublic class PetclinicSpringApplication {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        SpringApplication.run(PetclinicSpringApplication.class, args);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n3. **src/main/resources/data.sql** - Copy the SQL data from the existing data.sql file at src/main/runtimes/liberty/resources/META-INF/sql/data.sql (read it first and copy it here)\n\nAlso delete the old Java files that won't be needed:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java (replaced by PetclinicSpringApplication)\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageBundle.java (CDI qualifier, not needed)\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageProvider.java (JSF-specific)\n\nAlso delete all the DAO interfaces and implementations (will be replaced by Spring Data repositories):\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java\n\nAlso delete all EntityListener files (will use JPA callbacks directly):\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitListener.java\n\nAlso delete all the View interfaces and implementations (JSF managed beans replaced by Spring MVC controllers):\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerViewImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeViewImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyViewImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetViewImpl.java\n\nAlso delete the OwnerViewService files:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewService.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewServiceImpl.java\n\nAlso delete the old Owner2Model and OwnerFlowState and similar framework files:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/views/ (entire directory and all files)\n\nAlso delete EntityListenerLogger:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/EntityListenerLogger.java\n\nExecute all deletions using bash rm -rf commands, and create all files using the Write tool."}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":439,"cache_read_input_tokens":115650,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":439,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2429},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"17983ebd-5ffe-4ea7-a763-c5325de3e84e"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE Petclinic application to Spring Boot. I need you to create the following files. The base directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nIMPORTANT: First, remove all old Jakarta EE-specific directories and files that are no longer needed:\n- Delete the directory: src/main/liberty/ (and all contents)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/runtimes/ (and all contents) \n- Delete the directory: src/main/webapp/ (and all contents - JSF views are replaced by Thymeleaf)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/views/ (JSF views)\n- Delete the directory: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/views/ (JSF framework views)\n\nThen create these files:\n\n1. **src/main/resources/application.properties**\n```\nspring.application.name=petclinic\nserver.port=8080\nserver.servlet.context-path=/petclinic\n\n# PostgreSQL\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/petclinic_jakartaee_liberty\nspring.datasource.username=petclinic_jakartaee\nspring.datasource.password=petclinic_jakartaeepwd\nspring.datasource.driver-class-name=org.postgresql.Driver\n\n# JPA\nspring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create\nspring.jpa.show-sql=true\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.dialect=org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQLDialect\nspring.jpa.defer-datasource-initialization=true\n\n# Initialize database\nspring.sql.init.mode=always\nspring.sql.init.platform=postgresql\n\n# Thymeleaf\nspring.thymeleaf.cache=false\n\n# Actuator\nmanagement.endpoints.web.exposure.include=health,info\nmanagement.endpoint.health.show-details=always\n\n# Logging\nlogging.level.org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic=INFO\n```\n\n2. **src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/PetclinicSpringApplication.java**\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic;\n\nimport org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication;\nimport org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.SpringBootApplication;\n\n@SpringBootApplication\npublic class PetclinicSpringApplication {\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        SpringApplication.run(PetclinicSpringApplication.class, args);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n3. **src/main/resources/data.sql** - Copy the SQL data from the existing data.sql file at src/main/runtimes/liberty/resources/META-INF/sql/data.sql (read it first and copy it here)\n\nAlso delete the old Java files that won't be needed:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java (replaced by PetclinicSpringApplication)\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageBundle.java (CDI qualifier, not needed)\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageProvider.java (JSF-specific)\n\nAlso delete all the DAO interfaces and implementations (will be replaced by Spring Data repositories):\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDaoImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDao.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java\n\nAlso delete all EntityListener files (will use JPA callbacks directly):\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyListener.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitListener.java\n\nAlso delete all the View interfaces and implementations (JSF managed beans replaced by Spring MVC controllers):\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerViewImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeViewImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyViewImpl.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetView.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetViewImpl.java\n\nAlso delete the OwnerViewService files:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewService.java\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewServiceImpl.java\n\nAlso delete the old Owner2Model and OwnerFlowState and similar framework files:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/views/ (entire directory and all files)\n\nAlso delete EntityListenerLogger:\n- src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/EntityListenerLogger.java\n\nExecute all deletions using bash rm -rf commands, and create all files using the Write tool."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Cg4EkQsHXQjB92C3DoyZHW","session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"483454c8-688e-45a4-aafd-8b8579d6e556"}
