{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Cg4EkQsHXQjB92C3DoyZHW","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All tasks have been completed successfully. Here's a comprehensive summary:\n\n## Migration Summary: Jakarta EE to Spring Boot\n\n### Files and Directories Successfully Deleted\n\n**Jakarta EE-specific directories:**\n- `/src/main/liberty/` - Liberty server configuration\n- `/src/main/runtimes/` - Runtime-specific resources\n- `/src/main/webapp/` - JSF web application resources\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/views/` - JSF application views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/views/` - Owner JSF views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/views/` - Pet JSF views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/views/` - Pet Type JSF views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/views/` - Specialty JSF views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/views/` - Vet JSF views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/views/` - Visit JSF views\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/views/` - Framework JSF views\n\n**Jakarta EE application configuration files:**\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageBundle.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/MessageProvider.java`\n\n**DAO interfaces and implementations (replaced by Spring Data repositories):**\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDao.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDaoImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDao.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDao.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDao.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDaoImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDao.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDaoImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDao.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java`\n\n**EntityListener files:**\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerListener.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetListener.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeListener.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetListener.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyListener.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitListener.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/framework/db/EntityListenerLogger.java`\n\n**JSF View managed beans:**\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerView.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerViewImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeView.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeViewImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyView.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyViewImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetView.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetViewImpl.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewService.java`\n- `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerViewServiceImpl.java`\n\n### New Files Created for Spring Boot\n\n**1. `/src/main/resources/application.properties`**\n- Configures Spring Boot application with:\n  - Application name and server settings (port 8080, context path /petclinic)\n  - PostgreSQL datasource configuration\n  - JPA/Hibernate settings with create DDL strategy\n  - Database initialization enabled\n  - Thymeleaf template engine configuration\n  - Actuator endpoints for monitoring\n  - Logging configuration\n\n**2. `/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/PetclinicSpringApplication.java`**\n- Spring Boot main application class\n- Uses `@SpringBootApplication` annotation\n- Contains the standard Spring Boot main method to launch the application\n\n**3. `/src/main/resources/data.sql`**\n- Database seed data copied from the original Liberty runtime resources\n- Contains 60 lines of SQL INSERT statements for:\n  - 2 owners\n  - 12 pet types\n  - 5 pets\n  - 7 visits\n  - 7 specialties\n  - 2 vets with specialty associations\n  - Sequence restarts for all entities\n\nAll deletions and file creations have been successfully completed. The application is now ready for the next phase of migration, which will involve creating Spring Data repositories, Spring MVC controllers, and Thymeleaf templates to replace the deleted Jakarta EE components."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"ebe7fc7d-cd5f-4620-8fb7-99f3ac90a526"}
