{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_011hKtt9MFQXEPFrXRWEjtU1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01TUojPGABTpNAMp8HR1JmzU","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create entities and repositories","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE Petclinic app to Spring Boot 3. The base dir is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nThe entities already exist and use jakarta.persistence annotations which are COMPATIBLE with Spring Boot 3 (Spring Boot 3 uses Jakarta EE 10). However, I need to:\n\n1. Update the entity files to remove @EntityListeners references (since we deleted the listener classes) and remove the @XmlElement annotation from Specialty (requires jakarta.xml.bind which we're not including).\n\n2. Create Spring Data JPA repository interfaces\n\nPlease do the following:\n\n**A) Update existing entity files:**\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java\n- Remove the line: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db.OwnerListener;`\n- Remove the line: `@EntityListeners(OwnerListener.class)`\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java\n- Remove the line: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db.PetListener;`\n- Remove the line: `@EntityListeners(PetListener.class)`\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java\n- Remove the line: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeListener;`\n- Remove the line: `@EntityListeners(PetTypeListener.class)`\n- Remove the line: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;` (unused import)\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java\n- Remove the line: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db.VetListener;`\n- Remove the line: `@EntityListeners(VetListener.class)`\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java\n- Remove the line: `import jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.*;`\n- Remove: `@XmlElement(required = true)` annotation from the name field\n- Remove the import: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;` (unused)\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java\n- Remove the line: `import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitListener;`\n- Remove the line: `@EntityListeners(VisitListener.class)`\n\n**B) Create new Spring Data JPA repository interfaces:**\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface OwnerRepository extends JpaRepository<Owner, Long> {\n\n    List<Owner> findAllByOrderByLastNameAscFirstNameAsc();\n\n    @Query(\"select o from Owner o where o.searchindex like %:searchterm% order by o.lastName, o.firstName asc\")\n    List<Owner> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface PetRepository extends JpaRepository<Pet, Long> {\n\n    List<Pet> findAllByOrderByBirthDateAscNameAsc();\n\n    List<Pet> findByOwnerOrderByNameAsc(Owner owner);\n}\n```\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Optional;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface PetTypeRepository extends JpaRepository<PetType, Long> {\n\n    List<PetType> findAllByOrderByNameAsc();\n\n    Optional<PetType> findByName(String name);\n\n    @Query(\"select v from PetType v where v.searchindex like %:searchterm% order by v.name ASC\")\n    List<PetType> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.Vet;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface VetRepository extends JpaRepository<Vet, Long> {\n\n    List<Vet> findAllByOrderByLastNameAscFirstNameAsc();\n\n    @Query(\"select v from Vet v where v.searchindex like %:searchterm%\")\n    List<Vet> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;\nimport org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Optional;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface SpecialtyRepository extends JpaRepository<Specialty, Long> {\n\n    List<Specialty> findAllByOrderByNameAsc();\n\n    Optional<Specialty> findByName(String name);\n\n    @Query(\"select v from Specialty v where v.searchindex like %:searchterm% order by v.name asc\")\n    List<Specialty> search(@Param(\"searchterm\") String searchterm);\n}\n```\n\nFile: src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitRepository.java\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db;\n\nimport org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Repository\npublic interface VisitRepository extends JpaRepository<Visit, Long> {\n\n    List<Visit> findAllByOrderByDateAsc();\n\n    List<Visit> findByPetOrderByDateAsc(Pet pet);\n}\n```\n\nExecute all changes - edit the entity files to remove the EntityListener references, and create all repository files."}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4392,"cache_read_input_tokens":116089,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":4392,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":13426},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"68af6415-f878-4b00-8144-22a0300e1f57"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_011hKtt9MFQXEPFrXRWEjtU1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01GgskHofeU22UdbwBZNGh99","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create service implementations","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE Petclinic app to Spring Boot 3. The base dir is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nI need to rewrite the Service interfaces and implementations to use Spring annotations instead of Jakarta EJB. The old service files already exist and need to be overwritten.\n\n**Important**: The old Service interface files should be kept but updated. The old ServiceImpl files need to be completely rewritten.\n\nCreate/overwrite these files:\n\n**1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerService.java** (rewrite)\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n\nimport java.util.List;\n\npublic interface OwnerService {\n\n    List<Owner> getAll();\n    Owner findById(long id);\n    Owner addNew(Owner owner);\n    Owner update(Owner owner);\n    void delete(long id);\n    List<Owner> search(String searchterm);\n    List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner);\n    Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit);\n}\n```\n\n**2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerServiceImpl.java** (rewrite)\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\nimport org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db.PetRepository;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitRepository;\n\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Log\n@Service\n@Transactional\npublic class OwnerServiceImpl implements OwnerService {\n\n    private final OwnerRepository ownerRepository;\n    private final PetRepository petRepository;\n    private final VisitRepository visitRepository;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public OwnerServiceImpl(OwnerRepository ownerRepository, PetRepository petRepository, VisitRepository visitRepository) {\n        this.ownerRepository = ownerRepository;\n        this.petRepository = petRepository;\n        this.visitRepository = visitRepository;\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Owner> getAll() {\n        return ownerRepository.findAllByOrderByLastNameAscFirstNameAsc();\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Owner findById(long id) {\n        return ownerRepository.findById(id).orElse(null);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Owner addNew(Owner owner) {\n        owner.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Owner: \" + owner.toString());\n        return ownerRepository.save(owner);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Owner update(Owner owner) {\n        log.info(\"update Owner: \" + owner.toString());\n        return ownerRepository.save(owner);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public void delete(long id) {\n        ownerRepository.deleteById(id);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Owner> search(String searchterm) {\n        return ownerRepository.search(searchterm);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public List<Pet> getPetsAsList(Owner owner) {\n        return petRepository.findByOwnerOrderByNameAsc(owner);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    public Visit addNewVisit(Visit visit) {\n        visit.setUuid(UUID.randomUUID());\n        log.info(\"addNew Visit: \" + visit.toString());\n        return visitRepository.save(visit);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**3. src/