{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_011hKtt9MFQXEPFrXRWEjtU1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01GkFYU7WdmPzSXN5dXiNyrb","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Create DTOs and endpoint utils","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE Petclinic app to Spring Boot 3. The base dir is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output\n\nI need to update the DTO classes and EndpointUtil classes to replace Jakarta-specific annotations with Spring/Jackson equivalents. The existing files use:\n- `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty` -> Replace with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty`\n- `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbDateFormat` -> Replace with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonFormat`  \n- `jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.*` -> Replace with `com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat.xml.annotation.*` where needed, or just remove\n- `jakarta.ejb.EJB` / `jakarta.ejb.Stateless` -> Replace with Spring `@Component` / `@Autowired`\n- `jakarta.json.bind.*` (Jsonb, JsonbBuilder) -> Remove these methods, not needed in Spring (Jackson handles serialization)\n- `jakarta.xml.bind.*` (JAXB) -> Remove these methods, not needed\n\nPlease overwrite these files:\n\n**1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java**\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;\nimport jakarta.validation.constraints.*;\nimport lombok.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api.PetListDto;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.*;\n\n@Getter\n@Setter\n@ToString\n@EqualsAndHashCode\n@NoArgsConstructor\n@AllArgsConstructor\npublic class OwnerDto implements Serializable {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = 7995827646591579744L;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private Long id;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private UUID uuid;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String firstName;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String lastName;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String address;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String houseNumber;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String addressInfo;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String city;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String zipCode;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String phoneNumber;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private PetListDto petList = new PetListDto();\n}\n```\n\n**2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java**\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;\nimport lombok.*;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Getter\n@Setter\n@EqualsAndHashCode\n@NoArgsConstructor\n@AllArgsConstructor\npublic class OwnerListDto implements Serializable {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = 7608980315748812643L;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private List<OwnerDto> owner = new ArrayList<>();\n}\n```\n\n**3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java**\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.api;\n\nimport lombok.extern.java.Log;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.Owner;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db.OwnerService;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.Pet;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api.PetEndpointUtil;\n\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\n\n@Log\n@Component\npublic class OwnerEndpointUtil {\n\n    private final PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil;\n    private final OwnerService ownerService;\n\n    @Autowired\n    public OwnerEndpointUtil(PetEndpointUtil petEndpointUtil, OwnerService ownerService) {\n        this.petEndpointUtil = petEndpointUtil;\n        this.ownerService = ownerService;\n    }\n\n    public OwnerDto dtoFactory(Owner o) {\n        OwnerDto dto = new OwnerDto();\n        dto.setId(o.getId());\n        dto.setUuid(o.getUuid());\n        dto.setFirstName(o.getFirstName());\n        dto.setLastName(o.getLastName());\n        dto.setAddress(o.getAddress());\n        dto.setAddressInfo(o.getAddressInfo());\n        dto.setHouseNumber(o.getHouseNumber());\n        dto.setCity(o.getCity());\n        dto.setZipCode(o.getZipCode());\n        dto.setPhoneNumber(o.getPhoneNumber());\n        List<Pet> petList = ownerService.getPetsAsList(o);\n        dto.setPetList(this.petEndpointUtil.dtoListFactory(petList));\n        return dto;\n    }\n\n    public OwnerListDto dtoListFactory(List<Owner> sList) {\n        List<OwnerDto> dtoList = new ArrayList<>();\n        for (Owner o : sList) {\n            OwnerDto dto = this.dtoFactory(o);\n            dtoList.add(dto);\n        }\n        return new OwnerListDto(dtoList);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java**\n```java\npackage org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.api;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonFormat;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;\nimport lombok.*;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.api.PetTypeDto;\nimport org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.api.VisitListDto;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.Date;\nimport java.util.UUID;\n\n@Getter\n@Setter\n@ToString\n@EqualsAndHashCode\n@NoArgsConstructor\n@AllArgsConstructor\npublic class PetDto implements Serializable {\n\n    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1007513582768464905L;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private Long id;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private UUID uuid;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private String name;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    @JsonFormat(pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")\n    private Date birthDate;\n\n    @JsonProperty\n    private PetTypeDto petType;\n\