{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01TUojPGABTpNAMp8HR1JmzU","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All changes have been completed successfully. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Summary\n\n### A) Entity Files Updated\n\nSuccessfully removed EntityListener references and XML annotations from all entity files:\n\n1. **Owner.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/Owner.java)\n   - Removed import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.owner.db.OwnerListener`\n   - Removed annotation: `@EntityListeners(OwnerListener.class)`\n\n2. **Pet.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/Pet.java)\n   - Removed import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pet.db.PetListener`\n   - Removed annotation: `@EntityListeners(PetListener.class)`\n\n3. **PetType.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetType.java)\n   - Removed import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.db.PetTypeListener`\n   - Removed annotation: `@EntityListeners(PetTypeListener.class)`\n   - Removed unused import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.specialty.Specialty`\n\n4. **Vet.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/Vet.java)\n   - Removed import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.vet.db.VetListener`\n   - Removed annotation: `@EntityListeners(VetListener.class)`\n\n5. **Specialty.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/Specialty.java)\n   - Removed import: `jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.*`\n   - Removed annotation: `@XmlElement(required = true)` from the name field\n   - Removed unused import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.pettype.PetType`\n\n6. **Visit.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/Visit.java)\n   - Removed import: `org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.db.VisitListener`\n   - Removed annotation: `@EntityListeners(VisitListener.class)`\n\n### B) Spring Data JPA Repository Interfaces Created\n\nSuccessfully created all six repository interfaces with proper Spring Data JPA method declarations:\n\n1. **OwnerRepository.java** - with `findAllByOrderByLastNameAscFirstNameAsc()` and `search()` methods\n2. **PetRepository.java** - with `findAllByOrderByBirthDateAscNameAsc()` and `findByOwnerOrderByNameAsc()` methods\n3. **PetTypeRepository.java** - with `findAllByOrderByNameAsc()`, `findByName()`, and `search()` methods\n4. **VetRepository.java** - with `findAllByOrderByLastNameAscFirstNameAsc()` and `search()` methods\n5. **SpecialtyRepository.java** - with `findAllByOrderByNameAsc()`, `findByName()`, and `search()` methods\n6. **VisitRepository.java** - with `findAllByOrderByDateAsc()` and `findByPetOrderByDateAsc()` methods\n\nAll repositories:\n- Extend `JpaRepository<Entity, Long>` for full CRUD operations\n- Are annotated with `@Repository` for Spring component scanning\n- Include custom query methods using Spring Data JPA naming conventions\n- Include custom `@Query` annotations where needed for search functionality\n\nThe entities now use jakarta.persistence annotations which are fully compatible with Spring Boot 3, and the new Spring Data JPA repositories provide a clean, modern data access layer."}]}]},"parent