{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Fra49oeBCxkCozXS6hW3o8","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.api;\n     2→\n     3→import lombok.extern.java.Log;\n     4→import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n     5→import org.woehlke.jakartaee.petclinic.visit.Visit;\n     6→\n     7→import java.util.ArrayList;\n     8→import java.util.List;\n     9→\n    10→@Log\n    11→@Component\n    12→public class VisitEndpointUtil {\n    13→\n    14→    public VisitDto dtoFactory(Visit e) {\n    15→        VisitDto dto = new VisitDto();\n    16→        dto.setId(e.getId());\n    17→        dto.setUuid(e.getUuid());\n    18→        dto.setDate(e.getDate());\n    19→        dto.setDescription(e.getDescription());\n    20→        return dto;\n    21→    }\n    22→\n    23→    public VisitListDto dtoListFactory(List<Visit> eList) {\n    24→        List<VisitDto> dtoList = new ArrayList<>();\n    25→        for (Visit e : eList) {\n    26→            VisitDto dto = this.dtoFactory(e);\n    27→            dtoList.add(dto);\n    28→        }\n    29→        return new VisitListDto(dtoList);\n    30→    }\n    31→}\n    32→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GkFYU7WdmPzSXN5dXiNyrb","session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"9bd69952-8d2f-450a-80c5-d5c1bb8de1ab"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GkFYU7WdmPzSXN5dXiNyrb","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All 18 files have been successfully updated. Let me provide a summary of what was changed:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nSuccessfully migrated all DTO and EndpointUtil classes from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot 3. All 18 files have been updated with the following changes:\n\n### Changes Made:\n\n#### DTO Classes (14 files):\n1. **OwnerDto.java** - Replaced `@JsonbProperty` with `@JsonProperty`, removed `@XmlRootElement` and Jakarta XML/JSON imports\n2. **OwnerListDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n3. **PetDto.java** - Replaced `@JsonbProperty` with `@JsonProperty`, `@JsonbDateFormat` with `@JsonFormat(pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")`\n4. **PetListDto.java** - Replaced `@JsonbProperty` with `@JsonProperty`\n5. **PetTypeDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n6. **PetTypeListDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n7. **VetDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n8. **VetListDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n9. **SpecialtyDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n10. **SpecialtyListDto.java** - Same annotation replacements\n11. **VisitDto.java** - Replaced `@JsonbProperty` with `@JsonProperty`, `@JsonbDateFormat` with `@JsonFormat(pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")`\n12. **VisitListDto.java** - Replaced `@JsonbProperty` with `@JsonProperty`\n\n#### EndpointUtil Classes (6 files):\n1. **OwnerEndpointUtil.java** - Replaced `@Stateless` with `@Component`, `@EJB` with `@Autowired` constructor injection, removed Jsonb/JAXB serialization methods\n2. **PetEndpointUtil.java** - Same Spring annotations, removed Jsonb/JAXB methods\n3. **PetTypeEndpointUtil.java** - Replaced `@Stateless` with `@Component`, removed Jsonb/JAXB methods\n4. **VetEndpointUtil.java** - Same Spring annotations, removed Jsonb/JAXB methods, cleaned up Set to List conversion\n5. **SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java** - Replaced `@Stateless` with `@Component`, removed Jsonb/JAXB methods\n6. **VisitEndpointUtil.java** - Same Spring annotations, removed Jsonb/JAXB methods\n\n### Key Migration Points:\n- `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty` → `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty`\n- `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbDateFormat` → `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonFormat`\n- `jakarta.xml.bind.annotation.*` (JAXB) → Removed entirely\n- `jakarta.ejb.Stateless` → `org.springframework.stereotype.Component`\n- `jakarta.ejb.EJB` → `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired` with constructor injection\n- Removed all Jsonb/JAXB serialization methods (Spring Boot's Jackson handles this automatically)\n\nAll files are now Spring Boot 3 compatible and ready for use!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"955050b7-28b8-4b77-8946-199a62284a82"}
