{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01M12wsMS5BfNVStrn169mto","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully converted all six JAX-RS endpoint classes to Spring Boot REST controllers. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Conversion Summary\n\nAll six endpoint files have been successfully overwritten with Spring Boot 3 REST controller implementations:\n\n### Files Converted:\n\n1. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java**\n\n2. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java**\n\n3. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java**\n\n4. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java**\n\n5. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java**\n\n6. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java**\n\n### Key Changes Made:\n\n**From Jakarta EE JAX-RS to Spring Boot:**\n- Removed `@Stateless` (EJB) and `Serializable` interface\n- Removed `@Path` annotations (replaced with `@RequestMapping`)\n- Removed `@EJB` injection (replaced with `@Autowired` constructor injection)\n- Changed `@GET` to `@GetMapping`\n- Changed `@PathParam` to `@PathVariable`\n- Changed `@Produces(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)` to `produces = MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE`\n- Added `@RestController` and `@RequestMapping(\"/rest/...\")` at class level\n- Converted to constructor-based dependency injection with final fields\n- Removed XML endpoint methods (kept only JSON endpoints as specified)\n- Updated base path from `/owner` to `/rest/owner` (and similar for other endpoints)\n\nAll files now follow Spring Boot 3 best practices with constructor injection and are ready for use in your migrated application."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a6bcbcb-6946-47c7-9325-248dd051e737","uuid":"30396de3-5dd4-473b-a596-014345b56e25"}
