{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01AFYk7g2r37HtBfn9GCNu75","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All files have been successfully created. Let me provide you with a summary of what was created:\n\n## Summary\n\nI have successfully created all 17 files for your Spring Boot 3 migration of the Petclinic application. This replaces the old JSF/PrimeFaces views with Spring MVC controllers and Thymeleaf templates.\n\n### Spring MVC Controllers (5 files)\n\n**1. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/web/HomeController.java**\n- Handles home page (\"/\") and info page (\"/info\")\n\n**2. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/web/OwnerController.java**\n- Lists owners with search functionality\n- Shows owner details with associated pets\n\n**3. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/web/VetController.java**\n- Lists veterinarians with search functionality\n- Shows vet details with specialties\n\n**4. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/web/PetTypeController.java**\n- Lists pet types with search functionality\n- Shows pet type details\n\n**5. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/web/SpecialtyController.java**\n- Lists specialties with search functionality\n- Shows specialty details\n\n### Thymeleaf Templates (12 files)\n\n**Base Templat